data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. NEW AND IMPROVED PRICE....THIS HOME HAS EVERYTHING YOU NEED, NO REAR NEIGHBORS, NO FLOOD INSURANCE, GATED COMMUNITY WITH LOW MONTHLY HOA. THIS HOME BOAST LARGE OPEN FLOOR PLAN. WOW!!! Don’t miss this one! Location is KEY home is close to Suncoast parkway makes easy commute to Tampa, airport, beaches and more! As you walk through the front door to the open floor plan makes you feel right at home, kitchen has plenty of wood cabinets, granite counter tops, and newer stainless steel appliances, a great island for gatherings. Plenty of storage. A great in-law room, HOME OFFICE or guest bedroom downstairs with a full bathroom and upstairs features 4 large bedrooms and 2 more full bathrooms. Master bathroom has been updated. Roof is 13 years old, AC is 3 years old, newer water heater, newer appliances, ceiling fans, lighting and other fixtures. Exterior has been freshly painted and the back yard is nice size LARGE ENOUGH FOR A POOL and it is fenced. Conservation area in back so no rear neighbors. Community is gated, features pool, playground and more do not miss out on this 5/3/2 home on almost a 1/4 of an acre.
